---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Indiaesque"
  description="Learn about Indiaesque - your curated guide to authentic India experiences. Our story, mission, and the team behind your next adventure."
  includeFooter={false}
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-overlay">
      <span class="hero-location">ABOUT</span>
      <h1 class="hero-title">INDIAESQUE</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Connecting curious travellers with India's most authentic experiences since 2024.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <article class="article">
    <div class="article-content">
      <h2>Our Story</h2>
      <p>
        Indiaesque was born from a simple frustration: finding genuine, quality experiences
        in India shouldn't be this hard. Too many travel websites offer generic recommendations,
        outdated information, or hidden costs that only reveal themselves at checkout.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're travelers ourselves, and we wanted something different. A guide that tells you
        exactly what to expect, what you'll pay, and whether it's actually worth your time.
        No sponsored listings, no paid placements, just honest recommendations from people
        who've been there.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        We believe travel should be transformative, not transactional. Our mission is to
        connect curious travelers with experiences that reveal India's true character—the
        flavors, stories, crafts, and people that make this country unlike any other.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every experience on Indiaesque is personally vetted. We visit, taste, walk, and
        explore before recommending anything. If it doesn't move us, it won't make our guide.
      </p>

      <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Honest Pricing</strong> - All prices in INR, always. No surprise fees, no hidden charges.</li>
        <li><strong>Personal Curation</strong> - Every experience is vetted by our team. No paid placements.</li>
        <li><strong>Local Connections</strong> - We partner with local guides and artisans who share their expertise.</li>
        <li><strong>Practical Details</strong> - Duration, accessibility, best times to visit—the details that matter.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>
        Have a question about an experience? Want to suggest something we should check out?
        We'd love to hear from you. Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@indiaesque.com">hello@indiaesque.com</a>
        or visit our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <!-- NEWSLETTER -->
  <section class="newsletter">
    <div class="newsletter-inner">
      <h2 class="newsletter-title">Stay Up To Date By Subscribing<br/>To Our Newsletter</h2>
      <form class="newsletter-form">
        <input type="text" placeholder="FORENAME" />
        <input type="text" placeholder="SURNAME" />
        <input type="email" placeholder="EMAIL ADDRESS" required />
        <button type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section class="contact">
    <h3 class="contact-title">Contact</h3>
    <p class="contact-phone">+91 00000 00000</p>
    <p class="contact-address">Indiaesque &bull; Address Line 1<br/>Address Line 2 &bull; 110001</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER LINKS -->
  <section class="foot-links">
    <div class="foot-col">
      <h4>Destinations</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/delhi/">Delhi</a></li>
        <li><a href="/jaipur/">Jaipur</a></li>
        <li><a href="/mumbai/">Mumbai</a></li>
        <li><a href="/goa/">Goa</a></li>
        <li><a href="/varanasi/">Varanasi</a></li>
        <li><a href="/kerala/">Kerala</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="foot-col">
      <h4>Collections</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Food Tours</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Heritage</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Cooking</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Markets</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Day Trips</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Art & Craft</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COPYRIGHT -->
  <footer class="copyright">
    <p>&copy; Indiaesque {new Date().getFullYear()}</p>
    <p class="credit">Designed & Built in India</p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 300px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a9d8f 0%, #1a6b61 100%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }
  .hero-overlay {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 60px 20px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-location {
    display: block;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .hero-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 15px;
  }
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ARTICLE */
  .article {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 30px 20px;
  }
  .article-content {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
  }
  .article-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 40px 0 20px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }
  .article-content h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  .article-content p {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .article-content ul {
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .article-content li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .article-content a {
    color: #e07060;
  }
  .article-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* NEWSLETTER */
  .newsletter {
    background: #2a9d8f;
    padding: 50px 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .newsletter-inner {
    max-width: 320px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .newsletter-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 0 30px;
  }
  .newsletter-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .newsletter-form input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border: none;
    background: #fff;
    color: #333;
  }
  .newsletter-form input::placeholder {
    color: #aaa;
  }
  .newsletter-form button {
    padding: 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border: none;
    background: #e07060;
    color: #fff;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .newsletter-form button:hover {
    background: #c85a4a;
  }

  /* CONTACT */
  .contact {
    padding: 40px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }
  .contact-title {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0 15px;
  }
  .contact-phone {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .contact-address {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* FOOTER LINKS */
  .foot-links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .foot-col {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .foot-col h4 {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0 15px;
  }
  .foot-col ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .foot-col li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .foot-col a {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #666;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .foot-col a:hover {
    color: #e07060;
  }

  /* COPYRIGHT */
  .copyright {
    padding: 30px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
  }
  .copyright p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #999;
    margin: 0 0 5px;
  }
  .credit {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
</style>
